{"tid":2074032,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解唔睇樣就叫做真愛","createTime":"2020-06-21T19:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T15:32:54.000Z","uid":105396,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"69847f20d3638b20b926784746d5b95fc690335a","tid":2074032,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T19:59:54.000Z","msg":"點解唔睇樣就叫做真愛？<br />\n因為接受到佢外表嘅醜陋，鍾意佢嘅性格。所以代表真係鍾意佢個人？<br />\n但係外表都係佢個人嘅一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁如果我接受到佢性格嘅醜陋，鍾意佢嘅外表。其實都代表我係鍾意佢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定還是真愛只不過係人對愛情嘅完美化幻想、又或者係一個藉口。愛情就係愛情，就係要係呢段關係入面各取所需，世界上根本唔存在真愛呢樣嘢。<br />\n對我來講真愛就係肯幫對方擋子彈嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到底幾時會有人幫我擋子彈"},{"pid":"0a0a6a1d678a0d2714c7e66026a807b373b25f87","tid":2074032,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T20:00:13.000Z","msg":"其實我都係鳩噏 大家唔使咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f775b6e2c316abfd52d17a11f8875bc037bb25cb","tid":2074032,"uid":105396,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T20:01:26.000Z","msg":"話時話如果咁樣睇嘅話<br />\n友情應該係最脆弱嘅感情<br />\n你成日會聽到有人為自己屋企人、伴侶犧牲自己條命<br />\n但係好少聽到有人會為朋友犧牲自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df1c4d929227aefd42e854bcc28d5b9b55ad356","tid":2074032,"uid":218575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0a0a6a1d678a0d2714c7e66026a807b373b25f87","tid":2074032,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T20:00:13.000Z","msg":"其實我都係鳩噏 大家唔使咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T20:01:37.000Z","msg":"ok 拉！"},{"pid":"a416c9d2e5ff139418104e3d5c8c676a0b2b989c","tid":2074032,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2df1c4d929227aefd42e854bcc28d5b9b55ad356","tid":2074032,"uid":218575,"like":2,